Subject: [PATCH 1/3] Replace Idle function with standard VBI interface

Since vbiCtxctl isn't the standard VBI 2.0 interface, so replace
it with vbiIdle() in power_save function.

Signed-off-by: Yang Shi <yang.shi@windriver.com>
---
 arch/powerpc/kernel/wrhv.c |    2 +-
 1 files changed, 1 insertions(+), 1 deletions(-)

diff --git a/arch/powerpc/kernel/wrhv.c b/arch/powerpc/kernel/wrhv.c
index 704dec6..ab5dad5 100644
--- a/arch/powerpc/kernel/wrhv.c
+++ b/arch/powerpc/kernel/wrhv.c
@@ -177,7 +177,7 @@ unsigned long __init wrhv_find_end_of_memory(void)
 void wrhv_power_save(void)
 {
 	local_irq_enable();
-	vbiCtxctl(VBI_CTXCTL_IDLE, 1, 0);
+	vbiIdle(1);
 }
 
 void wrhv_restart(void)
